{"analytics_identifier":"PC1371","base_path":"/government/organisations/sheffield-forgemasters-international-ltd","content_id":"4930da96-9a35-493a-9a75-57402247e93d","description":"Sheffield Forgemasters is a heavy engineering company specialising in technically complex large-scale castings, forgings, and related advanced engineering technologies. It offers end-to-end manufacture for steel production from a single site in the UK. Tracing its origins back over 200 years, Sheffield Forgemasters has consistently been a market leader in the UK steel industry, bringing innovation to complex manufacturing and forging processes in areas that are key suppliers in the UK’s civil and defence sector as well as operating in global markets. Sheffield Forgemasters International Ltd is a public corporation of the Ministry of Defence .","details":{"acronym":"","alternative_format_contact_email":"DDC-MODInternet@mod.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Sheffield Forgemasters is a heavy engineering company specialising in technically complex large-scale castings, forgings, and related advanced engineering technologies. It offers end-to-end manufacture for steel production from a single site in the UK. Tracing its origins back over 200 years, Sheffield Forgemasters has consistently been a market leader in the UK steel industry, bringing innovation to complex manufacturing and forging processes in areas that are key suppliers in the UK’s civil and defence sector as well as operating in global markets.</p>\n\n<p>Sheffield Forgemasters International Ltd is a public corporation of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/ministry-of-defence\">Ministry of Defence</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"ministry-of-defence","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Sheffield Forgemasters International Ltd"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organ